ca.corefacility.gview.map.gui
Class GUIUtility

java.lang.Object
  ca.corefacility.gview.map.gui.GUIUtility

public class GUIUtility
extends java.lang.Object

Provides utility for the GUI. Contains many constants needed by various GUI components. Initializes various listeners. Provides access to various listeners.
